    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1765086019</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Wetlands of the coastal plains</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sumpfgebiete der Küstenebenen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Marécages des plaines côtières</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Wetlands das planícies litorais</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Wetlands delle pianure litoranee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Υγρότοποι των παράκτιων πεδιάδων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Wetlands de los llanos costeros</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This Carolina Environmental Diversity Explorations "virtual field trip" explores the various wetlands of North Carolina's coastal plain and the plant communities found there.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses Carolina virtuellen, welches die 
Klimaverschiedenartigkeit-Erforschungen "Reise" auffangen, 
erforscht die verschiedenen Sumpfgebiete Nord-Carolina von 
Küstenebene und von Betriebsgemeinschaften, die dort gefunden werden.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les explorations environnementales "voyage de 
cette diversité de la Caroline de zone virtuel" explore les divers 
marécages de la plaine côtière du nord de la Caroline et des
communautés d'usine trouvées là.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">As explorações ambientais "desengate desta 
diversidade de Carolina de campo virtual" exploram os vários wetlands
da planície litoral de North.carolina e das comunidades da planta 
encontradas lá.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Le esplorazioni ambientali "viaggio di questa 
diversità della Carolina di campo virtuale" esplora i vari wetlands 
della pianura litoranea del North.carolina e delle Comunità della 
pianta trovate là.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εξερευνήσεις "εικονικό ταξίδι αυτής της 
ποικιλομορφίας της Καρολίνας οι περιβαλλοντικές πεδίων" 
εξερευνούν τους διάφορους υγρότοπους παράκτιου σαφούς της 
βόρειας Καρολίνας και οι κοινότητες εγκαταστάσεων βρήκαν εκεί.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Las exploraciones ambientales "disparo al campo de
esta diversidad de Carolina virtual" exploran los varios wetlands del 
llano costero de Carolina del Norte y de las comunidades de la planta 
encontradas allí.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Wissenschaft und Technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La Science et technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciência e tecnologia</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienza e tecnologia</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Επιστήμη και τεχνολογία</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencia y tecnología</string>
          </keyword>
